      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. This specimen utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection to the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been properly maintained with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded powerflex bushings to ensure torsional rigidity under lateral load. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the valvetrain remains within factory tolerances. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the performance metrics are sharp, with the suspension geometry dialed for neutral handling and the throttle response remaining exceptionally crisp.",
